## FOHI (Flash of Hardcoded Inconsistency) Risk

Some components NOT modified in this plan will still have hardcoded colors visible in dark mode:
- **Badge.tsx**: `bg-green-100 text-green-700`, etc. These will look slightly "pastel on dark" but remain readable.
- **Toast.tsx**: `bg-green-600`, `bg-red-600` -- solid colors that work on any background.
- **TrialBanner.tsx**, **StatCard.tsx**, **SubscriptionStatusCard.tsx** -- semantic colored alerts that remain functional.
- **Various page-level `border-slate-*`** in MerchantClients, MerchantRewards, etc.

These can be addressed in a follow-up pass. The core experience (backgrounds, text, cards, navigation, inputs, modals) will switch cleanly.

